ARCC :: Home



























ARCC


















Ares CapitalCorporation
Ares CapitalCorporation


Ares Capital Corporation ("Ares Capital" or “ARCC”) is a leading specialty finance company that provides one-stop solutions to meet the distinct and underserved financing needs of private middle-market companies across diverse industries.  ARCC is the largest business development company by both market capitalization and total assets, with approximately $12.0 billion of total assets (NASDAQ: ARCC).(2)



Our Strategic acquisition of American capital, ltd. Closed on January 3, 2017  ►










FocusedObjective
Our mission is to create long-term value for our shareholders through an attractive dividend(1) and solid investment performance across economic cycles.







ExperiencedManagement
ARCC is externally managed by a subsidiary of Ares Management, L.P. (NYSE:ARES) ("Ares"), a publicly traded, leading global alternative asset manager.







DifferentiatedStrategy
ARCC pursues strong risk-adjusted returns, leveraging its disciplined investment philosophy, broad origination, multi-asset class expertise and creative structuring capability.













The Broader Ares Firm


ARCC is externally managed by Ares Capital Management LLC, a subsidiary of Ares.

