ARCC :: Portfolio



























ARCC




















ARCC
Portfolio


Portfolio Summary
Balanced Portfolio. Defensive Industries. Well Diversified.



As of March 31, 2017, Ares Capital Corporation's ("Ares Capital" or "ARCC") portfolio had a fair value of approximately $11.4 billion, and consisted of 316 portfolio companies backed by 166 different private equity sponsors. Ares Capital has a diversified portfolio in terms of issuer concentration, asset class, industry sector and geographic representation.

See Our Investments






